# Keyboard shortcuts

cmd+,           Edit config
ctrl+cmd+,      Reload config
ctrl+alt+,      Display current config
ctrl+shift+h    Open scrollback buffer in pager
ctrl+shift+g    Open last command output in pager
ctrl+shift+esc  Open kitty shell
cmd+r           Enter resize mode
cmd+k           Clear terminal
ctrl+shift+l    Circle through layout

# Tab
ctrl+shift+.    Move tab forward
ctrl+shift+,    Move tab backward
cmd+shift+i     Set table title 

# Scroll
cmd+up          Scroll line up 
cmd+page_up     Scroll page up 

# Check what bytes are sent
kitty +kitten show_key

# See also
# ./ghostty
